Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.43,0:00:12.25,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}There's no need to finagle, oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:16.28,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}We'll go all through the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:19.53,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I'll complain at the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.53,0:00:23.44,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}the balance is zero, oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.44,0:00:27.28,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}We'll whittle the days away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.91,0:00:31.37,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}When you open your heart a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:37.55,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}and pull someone close to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,0:00:49.40,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Your feelings will surely reach them deeper, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:01:00.19,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Hurry it up! Wring it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:05.63,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Though my legs are all tangled, they will surely take me far...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.86,0:01:11.15,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Even if I steal it and manage to grasp it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:15.38,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}If it isn't you, then what's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.71,0:01:20.37,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}So I'll go far into the distance...
Comment: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:27.77,OP2,,0,0,0,,OP End
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.46,0:01:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto's certainly different from you, Sasuke-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a dumber and gets in the way, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,At least he's not a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:01:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.95,0:02:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You foolish little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to kill me, resent me, hate me and continue to live your ugly life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And hang on to your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:49.42,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(343,238)}Sharingan Revived!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:49.42,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(490,570)}Finish move, Dragon Flame Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.75,0:02:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharingan revived. Finish move, Dragon Flame Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what I expect of the Uchiha clan. \NHis blood must be making him excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:03:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I should take my time and confirm his true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to live so I can kill my older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When that thought came to my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.07,0:03:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized that I was the one who was acting like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How can someone who can't put\Nhis life on the line at a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,kill that man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He was able to predict my movement and attacked accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be able to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun will set soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I must find him quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When night falls, it will be disadvantageous for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But, why in the world right now... what's his goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter, if he has come to this village, I will put an end to things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A replacement!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That was too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The Uchiha name is crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, I'm going to slowly beat you, and then kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharingan-controlled triple windmill blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Katon: Ryuuka no Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:09.68,TLnote,,0,0,0,,(Katon: Ryuuka no Jutsu; Fire Release: Dragon Fire Technique)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Paralysis?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect that you could use the Sharingan so well at your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You live up to the name of Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I do want you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're definitely his brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes hide even more potential than Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to see me again, get trough \Nthis exam as if your life depended on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeat the three Sound Village Ninja under my control.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The scroll!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What nonsense are you babbling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.86,0:09:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want to see your face ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.46,0:09:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You! What did you do to Sasuke-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave him a parting gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke-kun will seek me. He will seek me for power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I enjoyed seeing your various abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Sasuke-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.22,0:10:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke-kun, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke-kun's... Sasuke-kun's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Anko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an extremely dangerous S-class wanted criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'll kill you here even if it costs my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my duty as your former subordinate who learned everything from you, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.31,0:12:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hidden snake hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.29,0:13:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru, I'm going to borrow your left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That seal is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right... You and I are going to die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninja Art: Twin Snakes Sacrifice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You intend to commit suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,As you are a Special Jonin of the village, you can't be just using the forbidden Jutsu I taught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you it's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why have you come now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our reunion after so long, and yet you're awfully cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that you came to assassinate Hokage-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:15:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have enough subordinates for that yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I was planning on "reserving" some outstanding ones in this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A little while ago, I gave that same cursed seal as a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a boy that I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Selfish as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But that boy will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.93,0:15:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly... there's only a 10 percent chance that he'll survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But he might be like you, and not die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This kid, you really like him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still holding a grudge that I used you and threw you away?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike you, that kid will excel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, he is the boy that carries the abilities of an Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:16:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He has beautiful features and is\Na vessel who can become my heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If he survives, it will make things interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure not to cancel this exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Three people from my village are also under your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Make me enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If something happens to deprive me of my fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,consider it the end of Konoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We've secured food and water after spending half a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And now most teams have halted activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As we planned, this is the time we attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll split up into three and go scouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,However, whether we find other teams or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We return to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.41,0:17:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, break!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,His breathing is gradually getting regular...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But he still has a terrible fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to protect them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.66,0:17:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to tell this to Hokage-sama right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! At a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Paralysis Jutsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So you are here, Anko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You are ANBU members, but you arrived awfully late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That cursed seal has surfaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Orochimaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that it's come to this, we'll take you to Hokage-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, take me to the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever Orochimaru is seen here, a maximum security order is supposed to be put in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time for an exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,0:20:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'll tell the whole story later, so please call for Hokage-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Found you.
